name: AutoUploadFiles
tagline: A simple FTP uploader using JavaFX and Apache Commons Net.
body:
AutoUploadFiles is a Java project written by Maxim Berezin over the summer of 2016. It is a work-in-progress and continually worked on and improved.

Maxim Berezin is a student at University of Massachusetts Amherst studying Computer Science (BS).

This is an experimental use of GitHub Pages and Automatic Page Generator.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
